<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Welcome to Speakeasy!</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h1>Welcome to Speakeasy! 🌍</h1>
    <p>Learn languages the fun way with interactive games!</p>
  </header>

  <div class="container">
    <h2>How to Get Started:</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Pick a language you want to practice.</li>
      <li>Scroll through exciting games like Word Match, Flashcards, or Finish the Sentence.</li>
      <li>Read the description of the game to see what it's about.</li>
      <li>Hit the <strong>“Start Game”</strong> button to dive in.</li>
      <li>Follow the instructions, earn points, and hit a new high score!</li>
    </ol>

    <div class="button-container">
      <button onclick="location.href='/games'">Start Exploring Games</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
